Hi,

Well, here&#39;s my two cents:

If we want to rule out as much &quot;observer&quot; interference -- whether PK or whatever -- the fewer details we know, the better.

So, I&#39;m happy with a date, period.  I trust Frank&#39;s integrity to tell me if the event (if any happens) is a reasonable match, or not.

I&#39;d rather stumble onto the event on my own, than be accused of trying to mold the event -- or selectively focus on just certain aspects of it -- to fit criteria known ahead of time.

That&#39;s why I like things like the PEAR project (aka Global Consciousness Project); it&#39;s just numbers.  If and how it correlates... that&#39;s what gets interesting.

Cheerfully,
Fiona

